A fire has left parts of Charlotte Maxeke hospital in Johannesburg damaged. Scores of patients had to be moved to other facilities. eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu has more details. #DStv403​​ #eNCA Editor's note: This is a developing story JOHANNESBURG - A fire has left parts of Charlotte Maxeke Academic Hospital in Johannesburg damaged. Patients are being evacuated and moved to other facilities. Firefighters continue to battle the blaze, trying to contain the fire. The fire started on Friday morning and was contained but unfortunately reignited. Watch the video above for more details from the scene. eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu has more details. #DStv403​ #eNCA